name: Paperspine
overview:
As of December 12, 2009, Paperspine, Inc. went out of business. Paperspine, Inc. operates an Internet book service for book rentals and book sales. The company offers fiction books, such as children’s books, fantasy, gay and lesbian, literature, mystery and detective, romance, science fiction, short stories, suspense and thrillers. It also provides non-fiction books, such as art, biography and memoirs, body, mind and spirit, business and economics, cooking, family and relationships, gardening, gay and lesbian, health and fitness, history, house and home, personal finance, personal growth, pets, philosophy, poetry, psychology, psychotherapy, religion and spirituality, self-help, travel, and crime.

The company was founded in 2007 and is based in Issaquah, Washington.
